image_analysis.description: A photograph of a small bathroom or ensuite. The image shows a white vanity with a built-in sink and chrome faucets. Above the vanity is a large mirror reflecting the room. To the left is a glass-enclosed shower stall with white tiled walls and a drain on the floor. The floor outside the shower is covered in small, white, diamond-patterned tiles. A doorway frame is visible in the foreground, framing the shot. There are various toiletries on the vanity, including bottles and a tissue box.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot of a bathroom taken from a doorway.
